## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. After deploy, hit `https://<backend-url>/api/health` — should return `{"status": "healthy"}`
2. Open frontend URL — should load the login page
3. Sign up → Upload a CSV → Ask a question → Verify full flow works

### Manual Verification
- Test from a different device/browser to confirm it's publicly accessible
- Verify CORS is working (frontend can talk to backend)
- Check Render logs for any startup errors
